data.text: The information presented on this website may be revised and updated at any time as ongoing research progresses or as otherwise warranted. Use this site and the information provided on it subject to your own judgment. The Freer Gallery of Art and Arthur M. Sackler Gallery welcome information that would augment or clarify the ownership history of objects in their collections.
